'''额中回'''（{{lang-en|Middle frontal gyrus}}）是大脑[[额叶|额叶]]的一个[[脑回|脑回]]。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Middle Frontal Gyrus - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/middle-frontal-gyrus#:~:text=Middle%20Frontal%20Gyrus-,The%20middle%20frontal%20gyrus%20is%20a%20wide%20gyrus%20that%20lies,confusion%20in%20the%20anatomical%20literature.|accessdate=2021-04-09|work=|publisher=ScienceDirect|language=en}}</ref> 额中回与[[额下沟|额下沟]]、[[额上沟|额上沟]]、[[中央前沟|中央前沟]]相邻。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Middle frontal gyrus|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/middle-frontal-gyrus?lang=us|accessdate=2021-04-09|last=Gaillard|first=Frank|work=|publisher=Radiopaedia|language=en-US}}</ref>

== 功能 ==
有研究显示，额中回与人的识字和算术能力相关。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Differential contributions of the middle frontal gyrus functional connectivity to literacy and numeracy|url=https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-017-17702-6|last=Koyama|first=Maki S.|last2=O’Connor|first2=David|date=2017-12-13|journal=Scientific Reports|issue=1|doi=10.1038/s41598-017-17702-6|volume=7|pages=17548|language=en|issn=2045-2322|last3=Shehzad|first3=Zarrar|last4=Milham|first4=Michael P.}}</ref> 还有研究认为额中回是背部和腹部注意力网络的汇合地。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=A role of right middle frontal gyrus in reorienting of attention: a case study|url=https://www.frontiersin.org/articles/10.3389/fnsys.2015.00023/full|last=Japee|first=Shruti|last2=Holiday|first2=Kelsey|date=2015|journal=Frontiers in Systems Neuroscience|doi=10.3389/fnsys.2015.00023|volume=9|language=en|issn=1662-5137|last3=Satyshur|first3=Maureen D.|last4=Mukai|first4=Ikuko|last5=Ungerleider|first5=Leslie G.}}</ref>

